UID:event_313453514@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260314T055556Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260316T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260316T110000
SUMMARY:PDX Code & Coffee @ DeadStock Beaverton
DESCRIPTION:Portland Code & Coffee\n\\#\\# What to Expect:\n\nAt Beaverton Code and Coffee\, we currently have informal hosting with multiple rotating hosts. If you are a regular attendee (2+ times/month)\, feel free to ask more about it\, and I can add you as co-host!\n\nCode and Coffee is an inclusive\, informal co-working session. Drink some coffee\, bring your laptop\, and have engaging conversations. This is a great opportunity to learn from others\, share your knowledge\, and possibly collaborate on side projects\, online courses\, or even your day-to-day work tasks.\n\nStill uncertain? Let's chat on Discord! [https://discord.gg/JbGyY3bKTS](https://discord.gg/JbGyY3bKTS)\n\n\\#\\# Venue:\n\nThe Venue is Deadstock Coffee Beaverton\, who is graciously allowing us to host a space. WiFi\, power outlets. Check them out here: [https://maps.app.goo.gl/gH6zTjoTqssvE5rM9](https://maps.app.goo.gl/gH6zTjoTqssvE5rM9 "https://maps.app.goo.gl/gH6zTjoTqssvE5rM9")\n\n\\#\\# Agenda:\n\n* **9 AM - Arrival**\n* **11:30 AM - Wrapping Up**: You can stay longer\, but we'll officially be done!\n\n*After the introduction circle\, everything is self-organized. Find a social circle or grab a desk and code.*\n\n\\#\\# Links:\n\n* Join the Discord: [https://discord.gg/JbGyY3bKTS](https://discord.gg/JbGyY3bKTS)\n* Or [https://codeandcoffee.chat/](https://codeandcoffee.chat/)\n* If this link is down\, visit the main site [https://codeandcoffee.org/](https://codeandcoffee.org/) click on the Discord button!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/portland-code-coffee/events/313453514/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260220T235404Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260220T235404Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/9/6/0/a/600_524858410.jpeg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313331045@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260314T055556Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260320T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260320T110000
SUMMARY:PDX Code & Coffee @ Kiln
DESCRIPTION:Portland Code & Coffee\n\\#\\# What to Expect:\n\n*Please RSVP ahead of time as we only have a limited amount of space.*\n\nCode and Coffee is an inclusive\, informal co-working session. Drink some coffee\, bring your laptop\, and have engaging conversations. This is a great opportunity to learn from others\, share your knowledge\, and possibly collaborate on side projects\, online courses\, or even your day-to-day work tasks.\n\nStill uncertain? Let's chat on Discord!\n\n\\#\\# Venue:\n\nThe Venue is at Kiln\, who is graciously allowing us to host a space. WIFI\, power outlets. Check them out here: https://kiln.com/communities/portland/\n\nStreet Parking is available!\n\n\\#\\# Coffee:\n\nKiln has drip coffee and fixings available for it\, or if you want something a bit fancier you can head to Tiny's Coffee Shop across the street!\n\n\\#\\# Agenda:\n\n* **9 AM - Arrival:** Head to the kitchen (go left and go to the end of the hall) and find a spot! Look for the Code & Coffee signs on the table. Note: Doors do not open until 8:50AM\, you can walk straight in\, the front desk can direct you to the kitchen area.\n* **9:15 AM - Introductions**:\n* Share your name\n* Discuss your current projects or interests. If you don’t have a specific project\, share what intrigues you!\n* Mention your expertise and how you can assist others.\n* Are you job hunting or hiring? Let us know!\n* Community events you wanna plug. If none\, that's cool too.\n* **11 AM - Wrapping Up**: You can stay longer\, but we'll officially be done! In order to stay longer please ask about a one time guest pass at the front desk.\n\n*After the introduction circle\, everything is self-organized. Find a social circle or grab a desk and code.*\n\n\\#\\# Links:\n\n* Join the Discord: [https://discord.gg/JbGyY3bKTS](https://discord.gg/JbGyY3bKTS)\n* Or [https://codeandcoffee.chat/](https://codeandcoffee.chat/)\n* If this link is down\, visit the main site [https://codeandcoffee.org/](https://codeandcoffee.org/) click on the Discord button!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/portland-code-coffee/events/313331045/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260212T204901Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260212T204901Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/9/6/0/a/600_524858410.jpeg
END:VEVENT
